Reflection : Yani hamzaman ke dar hale Run shodan ast be an Class ezafe konim.
Bayad bedanim ke koja bayad az reflection estefade kard.

!! Agar bad moghe az an estefade konim baese kondie sistem mishavad
   Zira Reflection darad compiler ra dor mizanad.


!! Dar halate Reflection zamani ke mikhahim methodi ra invoke konim bayad hatman begoiem ke chandta vorodi darad
   va jense vorodihaye an chist ---> zira momken ast yek method chand Overload dashte bashad.

 !!!! Baraye gereftane Field dar halate Reflection farghi nadarad agar Field ha Private ya Public bashand.
